                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0261</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8442 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北方淄特开发鲁花客户的艰辛之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hardship Road of Northern Zi Te Exploiting Lu Hua Customer</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周涛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">淄博北方淄特化工有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北方淄特；项目谈判；客户开发战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Northern Zi Te; Project negotiation; Customer exploiting strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">淄博北方淄特化工有限公司，是集研发、生产、技术培训、销售、服务为一体的导热油、特种油、润滑油专业生产企业。本案例首先描述了北方淄特公司杨乃堂董事长如何在先失市场的情况下，成功地运用推销技巧，赢得鲁花公司信任，取得谈判成功的事件；接下来，北方淄特公司采取一系列的服务保障措施，确保了鲁花项目的顺利实施；然后，随着鲁花后续项目的不断开发，项目运作过程中遇到多项技术难关，北方淄特公司本着客户至上的服务宗旨，提供一揽子问题解决方案，真正实现了公司由卖产品到卖服务的营销模式转变；最后，案例对北方淄特公司的客户开发战略进行了总结和讨论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Zibo Northern Zi Te chemical company is a heat conduction oil, special oil, lubricants professional production enterprise that mainly contains R&amp;D, production, technical training, sales and service. This case firstly describes that Yang Nai-tang, the chairman of the Northern Zi Te, is how to use marketing techniques to win Lu Hua trust and achieve successful negotiations in the condition of losing market. Northern Zi Te nextly provides series of service guarantee measures, which ensures the smooth implementation of Lu Hua project. And then, with the Lu Hua subsequent project constantly exploited, the projict operation meets some technique problems, North Zi Te aims that the customer is highest, and provides a package problem solution scheme, which truly achieves the marketing model transformation that is from selling production to selling service. At last, the case summarizes and discusses the customer exploiting strategy of North Zi Te.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《客户管理》、《市场营销学》、《推销技巧》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对市场营销理念</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
